pipeline_summary.name: Data Transformation Pipeline
pipeline_summary.description: Google Cloud Dataform-based data transformation pipeline that orchestrates parameterized SQL workflow executions.

components.name: Initialize Pipeline
components.description: Marks the start of the pipeline execution.

components.name: Parse Input Parameters
components.description: Parses DAG run configuration and logical date, producing compilation configuration via XCom.

components.name: Create Dataform Compilation Result
components.description: Calls Google Cloud Dataform API to create a compilation result using parsed parameters.
outputs: Compilation result name (used for workflow invocation)

components.name: Trigger Dataform Workflow Invocation
components.description: Initiates a Dataform workflow execution using the compilation result, with async mode and incremental table refresh enabled.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after compilation result is created

components.name: Monitor Workflow Invocation State
components.description: Polls the Dataform workflow until it reaches a terminal state (SUCCEEDED or FAILED).

upstream_policy.description: Runs after workflow invocation is triggered

components.name: Finalize Pipeline
components.description: Marks successful completion of the pipeline after the sensor confirms termination.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after workflow state sensor completes
